ğŸ“ Overview

This project analyzes gender stereotypes using data from the international Towards Gender Harmony study.
The focus is on how sensitivity and competitiveness are perceived in women and men across different demographic groups.

The analysis is presented as an R Markdown HTML report.

ğŸ“‚ Data

- Source: Towards Gender Harmony (open-access)
- Observations: 33,313
- Countries: 62
- Years: 2018â€“2020
- Dataset link: https://osf.io/trkyc/files/w6bt3

ğŸ¯ Research focus

- Perception of sensitivity and competitiveness by gender
- Cross-cultural differences
- Differences by field of study and selected demographics
- Relationships between sensitivity and competitiveness

